        <div class="autocompleteWrapper">
         <label class="visuallyhidden" for="search-field">
          Search
         </label>
         <input autocomplete="off" data-profile="_default" id="search-field" maxlength="255" name="query" placeholder="Search..." type="text"/>
         <input id="Submit" name="Submit" type="hidden" value="Go"/>
         <a class="searchButton" href="/search/search-results.aspx?profile=_default" id="search-submit" role="button">

          </em>

       </div>
       <script>
        function killEvent(e){e&&e.stopPropagation&&e.stopPropagation(),window.event&&window.event.cancelBubble&&(window.event.cancelBubble=!0),e&&e.preventDefault&&e.preventDefault(),window.event&&(window.event.returnValue=!1)}
    $('div.autocompleteWrapper').on('click', 'ul.ui-autocomplete > li.ui-menu-item', function(e){     
    	window.location.href = $(this).find('a').attr("href");
  	});
    $("#search-field").keydown(function(e)
	{
  	 	if(e.keyCode === 13)
        {
            e.preventDefault();
			document.getElementById("search-submit").click();
        }
    });
    $("#search-submit").click(function(e)
	{
      	killEvent(e);
        var url = $(this).attr("href") + "&query=" + $("#search-field").val();
        window.location.href = url; 
	});
        
  var LiveSearch = (function ($) {
      "use strict";

      // private alias to settings
      var s;

      return {
          settings: function() {
              this.$searchCont    = $('.autocompleteWrapper');
              this.$searchInput   = $('#search-field');
              this.$searchResults = null;
              this.noResultsTxt   = 'There are no results that match your criteria.'
              this.minCharaters   = 2;
              this.resultsCount   = 5;
              this.basePath = '/search/search-results.aspx?profile=_default' + '&query=';
          },

          init: function() {
              s = new this.settings();

              this.setup();
              this.bindUIActions();
              this.navigateResults();
          },
          setup: function() {
              // build live results container
              s.$searchCont.append(
                  $('<ul/>', {
                      'class' : 'ui-autocomplete ui-front ui-menu ui-widget ui-widget-content'
                  })
                );


              s.$searchResults = $('.ui-autocomplete');
              s.$searchResults.hide();
          },
          addResultToList: function(node, count) {
              if(node) {
                  var path = s.basePath + node;

                  return $('<li class="ui-menu-item">').html('<a tabindex="'+ count +'" href="' + path + '">' + node + '</a>').appendTo(s.$searchResults);
              }
          },
          bindUIActions: function() {
              var timer;

              // Search input on keyup (typing in the input box)
              s.$searchInput.on('keyup', function(e) {
                  var $this = $(this);
                  var key = e.which;

                  // Down arrow key focus on the first item in the results
                  if (key == 40) {
                      s.$searchResults.find('li:first a').focus();
                  } else {
                      // Esc key
                      if (key == 27 || $this.val().length <= s.minCharaters) {
                          s.$searchResults.hide();
                      }                  
                    else if($this.val() !== '' && $this.val() != $this.attr('placeholder') && $this.val().length > s.minCharaters) {
                          // Add in a loader
						  
                          clearTimeout(timer);

                          // wait for 200 milliseconds (prevents flashing constantly between loader and results)

                            timer = setTimeout(function(){
                                $.get('//hertfordshirecc.funnelback.co.uk/s/suggest.json', { collection: 'hcc-web', profile: '__default', partial_query: $this.val() }).then(function(data) {
                                    // Empty out the current contents                                    
                                    // If we have results add them in else show a no results message
                                    if(data.length > 0) 
                                    {
                                      	s.$searchResults.empty();
                                      	s.$searchResults.show();
                                        for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
                                            LiveSearch.addResultToList(data[i], i);
                                        }
                                    } 
                                    else 
                                    {
                                      	s.$searchResults.hide();
                                    }
                                });                          
                            }, 200);                        
                      }
                  }
              });
          },
          navigateResults: function() {
              // down and up arrow key - go through the search results
              $(document).on('keydown', '.ui-autocomplete li a', function(e) {
                  var key = e.which;

                  // down arrow key
                  if (key == 40) {
                      e.preventDefault();
                      $(':focus').parent().next().find('a').focus();
                  }

                  // up arrow key
                  if (key == 38) {
                      e.preventDefault();
                      $(':focus').parent().prev().find('a').focus();
                  }
              });
          }
      };
  })(jQuery);


  jQuery(document).ready(function() {
      LiveSearch.init();
  });
       </script>
